data.value: SACNASP is contnuing to see an increase in the registraton of younger scientsts. SACNASP has in the past few years engaged with matric students through publicatons such as the career guide and events such as Natonal Science Week. In additon, there has been a concerted marketng drive aimed at students which provides students with informaton about the need to register with a professional body. The CMP programme is well positoned to grow the youth component of SACNASP’s registered scientsts.
